            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini nostri Iesu [Christi] dei aeterni. <persName
                            ref="#people/9" key="#Emperor/king">Hlotharius</persName> divina
                        ordinante providentia <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus.
                        Dignum est, ut imperialis maiestas procerum s[uorum] peticio[nibus tanto]
                        libentius [annuat easque ann]uendo adimpleat, quanto eos viderit ac noverit
                        in suis obsequiis persistere efficaces. Igitur omnibus [fidelibus sancte
                        dei] eclesie ac nostris presentibus [videlicet et] futuris notum sit, quia
                            <persName ref="#people/3924" key="#Bishops">Ioseph</persName>
                        venerabilis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/563"><orgName ref="#juridical_persons/404"
                                >[Ae]poredie</orgName></placeName> nostram deprecatus est
                        clementiam, ut cuidam fideli nostro <rs key="#Deacons">diacono</rs> scilicet
                            [<persName
                            key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Deacons"
                            ref="#people/3943">Godeberto</persName>] aliquid <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property">de rebus nostris in regno [I]talic[o]</rs>, hoc
                        est <rs key="#Areas">areas duas sibi invicem coherentes</rs>, ad proprium
                        concederemus; habetque prima area in longitudine pedes [XII, in latitudine
                        XXVI, et <rs key="#Confinia">cho]eret illi ab uno latere </rs>[...] sancte
                            <rs key="#Churches">eclesie</rs>, ab altero <rs key="#Houses">casa</rs>
                        <persName key="#Houses #Confinia"><name ref="Iohannes"
                            >Iohannis</name></persName> et <persName key="#Houses #Confinia"><name
                                ref="Adroaldus">Adroaldi</name></persName>, ab uno capite casa
                            <orgName key="#Houses #Confinia #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3514"><rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs> de
                            Sexto</orgName>, ab altero [ingre]ss[us interia]cens [do]m[us <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/138" key="#Domus #Confinia #Mother_churches"
                            >episcopa]tus [Lunensi]s</orgName> [eidem] areae; secunda habet in
                        longitudine pedes XLI, in latitudine vigintiquinque, coheret illi ab uno
                        capite via, [ab alio casa Adroaldi et Iohannis, ab uno latere casa
                        m]onasterii de Sexto, ab altero casa <orgName
                            key="#Houses #Confinia #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/1406"
                            >monasterii Senatoris</orgName> sive que illis alia coherent. [Has
                        designatas areas cum possessionibus et ingressibus] ac usum putei cum horto
                        deprecatus est nos iam dicto diacono iure proprietario tribui. Cuius
                        peticionem [adimplere s]tatuentes has mansuetudinis [nostre litteras fieri
                        decrevimus], per quas memorato Godeberto diacono <placeName ref="#places/65"
                            >Papiensi</placeName> areas supra scriptas, sicut superius insertum
                            est,<rs key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals">
                            iure proprietario concedimus</rs> habendum, ut quicquid vo[luerit vel]
                        elegerit habeat ex eis potestatem faciendi, sicut de reliquis proprietatis
                        sue rebus, ita dumtaxat, ut nusquam a nostra abscedat fidelitate, sed
                        immobiliter in nostris perseveret iugiter fixus obsequiis. Et ut hec nostre
                        largitionis vel confirmationis auctoritas [firma stabilisque] permaneat,
                        manu nostra su[bter eam firmavimus et anuli nostri impres]sione adsignari
                        iussimus. Signum domni Hlotharii serenissimi augusti. <persName
                            key="#Notary"><name ref="Rodmundus">Hrodmundus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> advicem <persName ref="#people/3908"
                            >Hilduini</persName> recognovit. Data VIII id. iul. anno Christo
                        propitio imperii Hlotarii pii imperatoris in Italia XXVII et in Francia VII,
                        indictione VIII; actum <placeName ref="#places/83"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Function #Residential #Palatium"
                            >Aquisgrani</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Function #Residential #Palatium"
                            >palatio regio</rs>; in dei nomine feliciter amen.</ab>
